Class RelatedProcess

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.devgateway.ocds.persistence.mongo.RelatedProcess

  • public class RelatedProcess
extends java.lang.Object
    Related Process

    A reference to a related contracting process: generally one preceding or following on from the current process.

private java.lang.String scheme
        Scheme

When cross-referencing information also published using OCDS, an Open Contracting ID (ocid) should be used.
